$ Oracle SQL - DDL statements

DDL Statements:
`analyze`, `associate statistics`, `audit`, `comment`, `create ...`, `disassociate statistics`, `drop ... `, `flashback ... `, `grant`, `noaudit`, `purge`, `rename`, `revoke`, `truncate`

Statements beginning with `alter` except `alter session` and `alter system` statements (which are session control and system control statements respectively)
are also DDL statements.


